UI Tests:
1. Login with valid email and password -> user is logged in
2. Login with invalid email and valid password -> error message
3. Login with valid email and invalid password -> error message

After Login
1. User creates new project -> verify if new project is created
2. User adds new task -> new task is created and displayed
3. User can edit created task -> the task is edited
4. User adds comment to the created task -> the comment is added
5. User can edit the comment -> the comment is edited
6. User can drag the task to the Done column -> the task is closed


API Tests:

1. Create new user
2. Edit created user
3. Create new project
4. Edit new project
5. Create new task
6. Edit created task
7. Delete created task
8. Delete created project
9. Delete created user



